<F P=100> National Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   State Property To Be Transferred to Local Authorities </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    State Property To Be Transferred to Local Authorities </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2905091894 Kiev Radio Ukraine World Service in Ukrainian 
0700 GMT 29 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2905091894 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev Radio Ukraine World Service </F>
<F P=105>  Ukrainian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] As has been reported by the press service of the 
president of Ukraine and the Cabinet of Ministers, the 
government has approved a resolution on converting state-owned 
property into the communal property of oblasts and the cities of 
Kiev and Sevastopol. The resolution contains a detailed list of 
incomplete construction facilities, children's pre-school 
institutions, health protection establishments, housing and 
utilities. Relevant ministries, departments, and corporations 
are to ensure that the above conversion be completed by 1 July 
this year. 

</TEXT>

