<H3> <TI>   Yeltsin Meets With Border Guards Chief </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Yeltsin Meets With Border Guards Chief </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PM3005130394 Moscow TRUD in Russian 28 May 94 p 1 </F>
