<F P=106> [Yuriy Dmitriyev report under the general heading: </F>
"Greeting to Border Guards"] 
  [Text] On the eve of the Russian Border Guards' holiday 
B.N. Yeltsin met with Colonel General A.I. Nikolayev, commander 
in chief of the Border Guards, and command personnel. Leaders 
of districts and groups of troops came from all over the country 
to meet with the president. The meeting took place in the 
Lubyanka building and at the Dzerzhinskiy Club. The president 
briefed the troops on Russia's current border policy. 

</TEXT>

