improve the situation and take the initiative. 
  Another round of quadripartite talks on a settlement of the 
Georgian-Abkhaz conflict is to open in Sochi tomorrow, 30 May. 
The talks will discuss the return of refugees to their homes, 
initially in Gali rayon. 

