  [Text] Moscow, RIA, May 30 -- The State Duma and the 
Russian Federation Council are due to consider the issue of 
potential financing Sevastopol as the main base of the Black Sea 
Fleet during its forthcoming sessions, a RIA correspondent was 
told by Viktor Semenov, chairman of the city council of 
