<H3> <TI>   Federation Council Endorses Ossetia State of Emergency </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Federation Council Endorses Ossetia State of Emergency </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD3105150894 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 1425 
GMT 31 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD3105150894 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [By ITAR-TASS parliamentary correspondent Lyudmila Yermakova] </F>
  [Text] Moscow, 31 May (ITAR-TASS) -- The Russian Federation 
president's edict "On the introduction of a state of emergency 
on part of the territory of the Republic of North Ossetia and 
the Ingush Republic" was endorsed by the Federation Council 
today. The state of emergency in the conflict zone is being 
extended to 31 July. 
  Deputies decided to set up a monitoring commission which 
will 
verify that the stipulations of the presidential edict are 
implemented. 

</TEXT>

