  [Text] Today Armenian Vice President Gagik Arutyunyan 
received Mir Ahmad Sadat, head of the Standards and Industrial 
Research Institute of the Islamic Republic of Iran; [name 
indistinct], deputy head of the metal production department of 
the institute; and [name indistinct], of the [word indistinct] 
