<H3> <TI>   Parliament Creates Commission To Fight `Mafia' </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Parliament Creates Commission To Fight `Mafia' </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC0106153494 Yerevan SNARK in English 1620 GMT 31 May 94 </F>
