<H4>    Yeltsin </H4>


<TEXT>
May Attend EU Corfu Meeting 

<F P=102> LD0106152794 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1331 GMT 1 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD0106152794 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>
