<H3> <TI>   Chernomyrdin To Continue Working on Economic Edicts </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Chernomyrdin To Continue Working on Economic Edicts </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0106134794 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1301 GMT 1 Jun 94 </F>
