<H3> <TI>   Labor Minister Urges `Practical' Approach To Wages </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Labor Minister Urges `Practical' Approach To Wages </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PM0106144594 Moscow ROSSIYSKIYE VESTI in Russian 28 May 94 p 
1 </F>

<F P=103> PM0106144594 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ROSSIYSKIYE VESTI </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


